lyrics:
[Verse]
Thedas and Sejan, the cool kids in town
With their energy, they never let us down
Together they conquer each challenge they face
Bringing joy and laughter, spreading their embrace

[Chorus]
Oh, Thedas and Sejan, shining so bright
The world is yours, you're the stars of the night
You light up our lives, with love so pure
Thedas and Sejan, forever secure
